# simple-heroku

A compojure skeleton that can be deployed on Heroku

## Usage
locally can be run with
lein ring server
or
lein run -m simple-heroku.core
lein run -m simple-heroku.core 8001 or whatever valid port

## Heroku
Create an account & follow instructions
clone the repo
heroku create --stack cedar
git push heroku master
heroku scale web=1
heroku open

